data.description: STILL AVAILABLE for offers with no contingency of selling home.     Discover living in the thriving Van Alstyne area with this new listing! This charming home boasts a stunning front elevation, a spacious front porch, and an expansive backyard for outdoor enjoyment. The well-designed office at the front features beautiful French doors, creating an inviting workspace. Master downstairs with 3 bedrooms up along with large game room.The first and second floor is wired for theatre system offering a contemporary touch to your lifestyle.The oversized garage will fit two cars while leaving enough room for a workshop. Enjoy convenience with quick access to the highway, retail options, and restaurants. A new park called Central Social District with a Splash pad and concert hall finished in May 2022 and an additional park next to the neighborhood coming soon. Brand new High School slated to open next year! Don't miss the chance to make this updated gem your new home!
